a broken one~
A broken one shambles through the corrupted undergrowth.
~
A humanoid figure whose features have been degraded by prolonged exposure to
the confusion mists and crystal resonance. The broken one's skin is waxy and
pale, preserved by the Withered magic that has simultaneously eroded its mind.
It moves without clear purpose, following patterns that may once have been
patrol routes or escape attempts, now repeated endlessly without understanding.
The eyes are open but unfocused, the face slack.
~
