#9618
broken one~
a broken one~
A broken one lurches among the blackened trees, its movements jerky and wrong.
~
Another victim of the Withered corruption, this broken one is further along
the degradation curve. Its clothing has rotted to rags, and the preservation
magic has given its skin a leathery toughness that compensates for the muscle
wasting beneath. It responds to movement with aggressive lunges, the fight-
or-flight reflex reduced to fight-only by the cognitive erosion that has
stripped away everything but base survival instincts.
~
