greater broken one~
a greater broken one~
A greater broken one towers among the corrupted trees, its bulk terrible.
~
The end-stage of the broken-one degradation, a creature that barely resembles
the humanoid it once was. The greater broken one is massive, its body swollen
by the preservation magic into a grotesque parody of strength. The skin is
bark-hard, the hands have fused into club-like appendages, and the face has
lost all individual features. It is alive, preserved, and almost entirely
mindless, responding to intrusion with overwhelming physical violence.
~
