mist-wolf withered~
a mist-wolf~
A mist-wolf stalks through the corruption, its form half-hidden in the haze.
~
A large canine predator adapted to the Withered-influenced zones, its fur
carrying the same violet tinge as the corruption mist it hunts within. The
mist-wolf moves with unnerving silence, its paws leaving no prints in the
spongy preserved ground. Its eyes glow faintly with reflected crystal
resonance, and its hunting strategy exploits the confusion effects to herd
prey into dead-end pockets where the pack can close.
~
