#9622
bark revenant withered~
a bark revenant~
A bark revenant drags itself through the contested band, bark-plated and relentless.
~
A creature that may once have been a treant, now fully corrupted by the Withered
influence. Its bark is blackened and cracked, weeping the same blood-colored sap
that marks the fire-scarred trees of the Ashen Lattice. The revenant moves
with grinding determination, its root-limbs tearing through earth and stone
with the slow, unstoppable force of growing wood turned to destructive purpose.
It is a Verdant creature weaponized by corruption.
~
