A miserable creature, a neogi that has failed to achieve master status and
been enslaved by its own kind. The slave's eight-legged body is thin and
scarred, its fur matted with filth, and its long neck droops with exhaustion.
Iron restraints around its front limbs connect to chains that allow limited
movement within the warren's slave pen.
~
