neogi ruler~
the Neogi ruler~
The Neogi ruler reclines on its web-throne, radiating cold authority.
~
The largest and most powerful neogi in the warren, occupying a web-throne of
its own construction. The ruler's body is massive for a neogi, its fur sleek
and dark, and its long neck carries the head with the rigid posture of absolute
authority. Jewelled objects hang from its web-throne, tribute from the warren's
slave-trading operations. The ruler's eyes are sharp and calculating, assessing
every creature that enters its presence as either useful or expendable.
~
