centaur male~
a male centaur~
A male centaur stands here, stone-tipped spear in hand.
~
A powerfully built centaur warrior, his human torso rising from a horse body
of deep chestnut. His face is weathered by forest life, and his hands grip
a stone-tipped spear with the ease of lifelong practice. The centaur's
expression carries the guarded neutrality of a people who have learned that
outsiders bring more trouble than benefit. Woven bark armor covers his flanks,
and a stone shield hangs from a leather strap across his back.
~
