A terrifying hybrid creature with the upper body of a muscular humanoid and
the lower body of a giant scorpion. Chitin plates cover its torso and limbs,
and its scorpion tail arches over its back, the venomous stinger glistening.
The manscorpian navigates the cave tunnels by scent, its antennae twitching
constantly as they read the chemical information encoded in the cave air.
~
