The largest and most powerful manscorpian in the colony, its body a monument
to the species' terrifying potential. The king's chitin plates are an almost
black shade of deep red, and its scorpion tail is massive, the stinger the
size of a short sword. A crown of chitin fragments from defeated predecessors
adorns its humanoid brow. The king's eyes burn with territorial intelligence,
and its every movement radiates the supreme confidence of an apex predator
in its own domain.
~
