yugoloth guardian~
a Guardian Yugoloth~
A Guardian Yugoloth blocks the cabin approach, its extraplanar form shimmering.
~
An extraplanar entity of terrible power, bound to guard the approach to
Ymmas's cabin. The yugoloth's form is roughly humanoid but wrong in every
proportion: too tall, too thin, with limbs that bend at angles that no
natural skeleton would permit. Its skin is a dark, metallic sheen that
reflects the forest light in distorted patterns, and its eyes are points of
cold fire that track every movement with inhuman precision. The binding
that holds it here is old and strong, the work of a summoner whose power
exceeds anything the forest's other residents command.
~
