ymmas~
the evil Ymmas~
The evil Ymmas stands in the sanctum, radiating controlled menace.
~
A figure of indeterminate age and considerable power, Ymmas occupies the cabin
sanctum with the casual authority of someone who has held this position for
longer than Kiess has existed. The mage's robes are practical rather than
theatrical, the garments of someone who values function over display. But the
eyes betray the truth: deep-set, luminous, and carrying the weight of decades
of arcane practice. Ymmas's hands move with the precise economy of a
spellcaster whose every gesture can invoke destruction.
~
