spider~
a giant spider~
A giant spider crouches in the heart of its web, still and watchful.
~
An enormous spider occupying the boundary zone between Verdant and Withered
influence, its body adapted to both environments. The spider's carapace
is mottled in patterns of healthy green and corrupted black, and its venom
is exceptionally potent, an adaptation to prey toughened by preservation
magic and crystal resonance. Its web spans multiple trees, a three-
dimensional hunting construct of architectural complexity. The spider
waits with the infinite patience of a creature that knows its prey will
come to it.
~
